Encapsulation is used at Page layer where by locators and page actions are given.
Base Test extends Driver Factory class - uses Inheritance concept.


Thread local concept to ensure parallel executions works as expected when more test cases are
present.


testng.xml browser name can be prioritized over config.properties browser by using prop.setProperty
in setup() in BaseTest class.

maven commands:
mvn --version

cd <projectpath>
mvn clean install -Denv="qa"

Jenkins:

Jenkins is used to run Tests in CI/CD, common machine should be present for all automation engineers.

to start jenkins :
java --jar jenkins.war -httpPort=8080

Tests are triggered by jenkins and run on dockerized grid.

BO Pipeline and ngrok web hook proxy server can also be setup, also jobs can be scheduled at respective time.



